i18n.cookieBannerSubTitle: TikTok uses cookies and similar technologies to provide, improve, protect and analyze our services. Essential cookies are necessary for our site to work as intended. By selecting "Allow all", you allow us to use optional cookies for additional purposes, such as measuring the effectiveness and relevance of ads, including personalized ads on TikTok.com, depending on your settings. Optional cookies also help us do other things, such as better measure the performance of our advertising campaigns off TikTok.com. Learn more about how we use cookies and manage your choices in our Cookies Policy.
